metadata.name: Her Palette #1. Florence
metadata.description:
A digital painting by Nataly Borich. Inspired with 1920s. 

The working digital palette around the main frame was used in the process of drawing to adjust thickness and colors of brushstrokes. It was remained in the final artwork as a part of the story.

The image is: JPEG, 18000x18000 pixels, 300 ppi, RGB.
